import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Box , Flex, Grid, Sticky, Absolute, Fixed} from '../lib'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"hello-world"}}>{`Hello world`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"box"}}>{`Box`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Hello, I'm a mdx file!`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Box} />
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />`} __scope={{props,Box,Flex,Grid,Sticky,Absolute,Fixed}}><Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" /></Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"flex"}}>{`Flex`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Flex justifyContent="space-between">
  <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
</Flex>`} __scope={{props,Box,Flex,Grid,Sticky,Absolute,Fixed}}>
  <Flex justifyContent="space-between">
    <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />
  </Flex>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"grid"}}>{`Grid`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Grid min="300px" gap="20px">
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
</Grid>`} __scope={{props,Box,Flex,Grid,Sticky,Absolute,Fixed}}>
  <Grid min="300px" gap="20px">
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  </Grid>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"absolute"}}>{`Absolute`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Absolute top={0} right={0}>
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
</Absolute>
<Absolute top={0} left={0}>
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
</Absolute>`} __scope={{props,Box,Flex,Grid,Sticky,Absolute,Fixed}} style={{height: '100px'}}>
  <Absolute top={0} right={0}>
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
  </Absolute>
  <Absolute top={0} left={0}>
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
  </Absolute>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"fixed"}}>{`Fixed`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={5} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Fixed top={0} right={0}>
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
</Fixed>
<Fixed top={0} left={0}>
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
</Fixed>`} __scope={{props,Box,Flex,Grid,Sticky,Absolute,Fixed}} style={{height: '100px'}}>
  <Fixed top={0} right={0}>
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
  </Fixed>
  <Fixed top={0} left={0}>
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" width="100px" />
  </Fixed>
</Playground></MDXTag>
